# Sandcastle's docker provider can read its own .env at this path, but in this
# project we keep secrets in the **repo-root** `.env` (raw values, see
# CLAUDE.local.md). `tsx --env-file=.env .sandcastle/main.ts` loads them into
# the Node process, and main.ts forwards them into the container via
# docker({ env }).
#
# Don't populate this file unless you specifically want a separate Sandcastle
# env source — leave it as documentation. Required vars:
#
#   ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=<sk-ant-...>   # for the Claude Code CLI inside the sandbox
#   GH_TOKEN=<ghp_...>               # PAT with `repo` scope for `gh` inside the sandbox
